<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Alex Rodriguez posted a heartwarming Instagram snap this week of his fiancee Jennifer Lopez and their respective daughters.</p>

<p>The 45-year-old former New York Yankee shares his children Natasha, 15, and Ella, 12, with his ex-wife Cynthia Scurtis.</p>

<p>Meanwhile the 51-year-old pop star shares her 12-year-old twins Max and Emme with her third ex-husband Marc Anthony with whom she is still friendly.</p>

<p>'My girls': Alex Rodriguez posted a heartwarming Instagram snap this week of his fiancee Jennifer Lopez and their respective daughters</p>

<p>Jennifer and Emme posed flanking Natasha and Ella in a sweet picture that Alex posted with the caption: 'My girls. #Emme #Tachi #Ella #Macha.'</p>

<p>Alex proposed to Jennifer last year and presented her with her fifth engagement ring - the previous four came from her three husbands and her ex-fiance Ben Affleck.</p>

<p>The new Instagram post comes after a group led by 'J-Rod' were outbid by hedge fund manager Steve Cohen to purchase the New York Mets.</p>

<p>'My Macha': Alex proposed to Jennifer last year and presented her with her fifth engagement ring - the previous four came from her three husbands and her ex-fiance Ben Affleck</p>

<p>Steve, whose net worth Forbes estimates at $14.6 billion, is said to have paid $2.4 billion in a deal first reported by Jon Heyman of MLB network on Twitter.</p>

<p>'Heard the #Mets sold for more than the $2.35B that has been reported. It is for between $2.4B and $2.45B,' the New York Posts' Joel Sherman tweeted Monday.</p>

<p>'The previous record for a North American sports team was the $2.275B that the Panthers were sold for to another hedge fund billionaire, David Tepper.'</p>

<p>Close but no cigar: The new Instagram post comes after a group led by 'J-Rod' were outbid by hedge fund manager Steve Cohen to purchase the New York Mets</p>

<p>'J-Rod,' as they are affectionately known to their fans, paid up $300 million themselves in their attempt to buy the team from Fred and Jeff Wilpon.</p>

<p>However they did snag a new house this July, dropping what Variety reported as $1.4 million for a three-bedroom home in the Los Angeles suburb Encino. </p>

<p>At the start of this year before the lockdowns Emme made a special appearance during her mother's Super Bowl halftime show co-starring Shakira.</p>
